name: DFSProxyRegistry
description: Checks Mcd registry and replaces the proxy addr if owner changed.

functionDecorators.name: changeAdmin
functionDecorators.description: Admin is able to set new admin.

parameterDecorators.name: _admin
parameterDecorators.description: Address of multisig that becomes new admin.

functionDecorators.name: changeMcdOwner
functionDecorators.description: Changes the proxy that is returned for the user. Used when the user changed DSProxy ownership himself.

functionDecorators.name: changeOwner
functionDecorators.description: Admin is able to change owner.

functionDecorators.name: getMcdProxy
functionDecorators.description: Returns the proxy address associated with the user account. If user changed ownership of Dsproxy admin can hardcode replacement.

functionDecorators.name: setAdmin
functionDecorators.description: Admin is set by owner first time, after that admin is super role and has permission to change owner.

parameterDecorators.name: _admin
parameterDecorators.description: Address of multisig that becomes admin.
